http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Visakhapatnam/Genpact-hires-39-students/article14019210.ece

The Genpact has selected 39 students from various colleges and given them away appointment letters during a two-day campus drive organised by Andhra Pradesh State Council for Higher Education, in association with the Andhra Pradesh Skill Development Corporation and the NASSCOM at PRISM Degree and PG College here. More than 1,000 students attended the campus drive held from Friday.Students who were in border levels of performance will be imparted with free training sessions by the Mind Map team under the guidelines of NASSCOM, under the youth empowerment programme.